
Quick Description

Usage Notes

Installation Notes
	- .vimrc


= [installation notes]

	- user
		- pre-installation requisites
			- you need flex
			- you must compile libpcap from sources (static)
		- build and install binary
			$ ./configure
			$ make && sudo make install
		- run tests
			$ make test
		- paste ./scripts/dotvimrc into ~/.vimrc
			$ cat ./scripts/dotvimrc >> ~/.vimrc
		- check that opening a .pcap file using vim allows text-based
			pcap trace edition

	- package management (maintainer)
		- re-create package
			- autoreconf
		- clean everything
			- make maintainer-clean
		- create dist
			- ./configure
			- make dist

